<h1>Update on Your Visa Letter Application</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @participant.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your interest in attending <strong><%= @event.name %></strong>.</p>

<p>Unfortunately, we are unable to provide a visa invitation letter for your application at this time.</p>

<% if @application.rejection_reason.present? %>
<h2>Reason</h2>
<p><%= @application.rejection_reason %></p>
<% end %>

<% if @can_reapply %>
<h2>You Can Reapply</h2>
<p>If you have addressed the issues mentioned above or have additional information to provide, you are welcome to submit a new application.</p>
<p><a href="<%= @reapply_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ec3750; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">Reapply Now</a></p>
<% else %>
<p>If you believe this decision was made in error, please contact us at <%= @event.contact_email %>.</p>
<% end %>

<p>We appreciate your understanding.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Hack Club Team</p>
